short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Extension that permits to show rarities on Deadrare marketplace

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Extension that permits to show ranks on Elrond collections on the Deadrare marketplace (https://deadrare.io/). New collections and features will be released soon. 

Actual available collections : ElrondApes.

If the ranking don't show up when arriving on the page, just reload it.
